Arkadiusz Chojnacki, the head of
research at Ipopema Securities SA, has left the Warsaw-based
brokerage.  The company has already chosen his successor and will make
it public soon, Stanislaw Waczkowski, a deputy Chief Executive
Officer of Ipopema, said in an e-mailed reply to questions from
Bloomberg News today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
